1. Molim te da mi *dokažeš* da si u pravu. (Please prove to me that you are right.)
2. Ako mi *dokažeš* da si radio na tom projektu, dobit ćeš bonus. (If you prove to me that you worked on that project, you will get a bonus.)
3. Ona će *dokazati* svoju nevinost na sudu. (She will prove her innocence in court.)
4. Ne mogu da *dokažem* svoju ljubav prema tebi. (I can't prove my love for you.)
5. Molim te da mi *dokazuješ* svoju vernost. (Please prove to me your loyalty.)
6. Ako hoćeš da *dokazuješ* svoju vrednost, moraš naporno raditi. (If you want to prove your worth, you have to work hard.)
7. On će *dokazivati* svoju teoriju tokom predavanja. (He will prove his theory during the lecture.)
8. Nisam uspeo da *dokazem* svoju nedužnost. (I failed to prove my innocence.)
9. Želela bih da mi *dokazeš* da si spreman da se žrtvuješ za mene. (I would like you to prove to me that you are ready to sacrifice yourself for me.)
10. *Dokazujući* svoje znanje, dobio je posao. (By proving his knowledge, he got the job.)